From 8ef5a1c44e254a3593048bba63dc780a9fc119a0 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Kol Crooks <kol.crooks@datadoghq.com>
Date: Mon, 4 May 2026 18:11:17 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] Phase 5: PR view with description, sidebar, activity, reply
 box

Replaces the Phase 4 placeholder PR pane body with the real PR view:
- Description rendered via base renderMarkdown (IMarkdownString).
- Sidebar cards: Reviewers / Checks / Labels / Stats. Reviewer state
  pills, check status glyphs with optional click-to-open details_url.
- Activity tabs: Discussion (issue comments) and Automation (timeline
  events, lazy-loaded on first click).
- Functional reply box that POSTs an issue comment via gh api and
  appends the new comment to the discussion timeline.

Provider extensions:
- IGhClient.apiPostJson(path, body) - gh api -X POST --input - with
  JSON-encoded stdin (form-encoded -f keys are wrong for endpoints
  that take arbitrary string bodies).
- IPullRequestProvider.getActivity(url) - issues/{n}/timeline mapped
  to AutomationEvent[].
- IPullRequestProvider.postIssueComment(url, body) - issues/{n}/
  comments POST returning the new Comment.
- getPullRequest now parallel-fans REST calls for issue comments,
  reviews, and check-runs to populate reviewers/checks/comments.
